{"tid":422603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大教授李立峯：八九民運可能是曼德拉效應下的錯記事情","createTime":"2017-10-03T08:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T01:12:47.000Z","uid":82640,"like":14,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6d62916cf9ddf7c60d994e70fa273b0fd70cb0","tid":422603,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"香港01洗腦真係好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n// 舉例說，我在幾年前開始進行關於香港人對六四的集體回憶的研究，試過對一些市民進行訪談，其中一條問題就是要讓他們憶述，1989 年 6 月 3 日晚上，他們在做什麼，以及在什麼情況下知道鎮壓的消息。每位被訪者的情況固然不完全一樣，但他們對當天晚上的回憶，在敍事結構上是高度一致的，就是先強調自己當時高度關注事件，情緒已經非常緊張，無時無刻在聽着電台或看着電視以獲知最新資訊，那天晚上亦是一樣，一直貼着媒體，所以亦差不多是第一時間得知消息。<br />\n<br />\n我無法分辨被訪者的回憶有沒有錯誤，但我們見到的是個人回憶背後有共同的敍事框架。在這種社會框架的影響下，如果有人當天晚上其實並不像自己多年後敍述的一模一樣，是絕對有可能的。同樣道理，如果一個強大的社會框架使很多人同時以為沒有發生過的事曾經發生，也是有可能的。//<br />\n<br />\n繼力撐食早餐成績好一文後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n李立峯又再證明支文大學垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曼德拉效應：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/122223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F122223&d=UZAdTXUFKOLvNuBFb7LfszCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b87bb624\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/122223</a><br />\n食早餐成績好：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01博評-政經社/56822/食早餐就有好成績-到底研究報告說了什麼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93%E7%A4%BE%2F56822%2F%E9%A3%9F%E6%97%A9%E9%A4%90%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%BD%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E8%AA%AA%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC&d=UZAdTXUFKOLvNuBFb7LfszCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=32e6b37b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01博評-政經社/56822/食早餐就有好成績-到底研究報告說了什麼</a>"},{"pid":"177d017b06d5080e2025149c698bf79d7bbb4c19","tid":422603,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85d2a9494ba91249864b766201592e174abab2ae","tid":422603,"uid":64146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要停止一切捐款"},{"pid":"282d80953d2963bfe34f6176efa06cc9b36d8591","tid":422603,"uid":103325,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"實情係當晚死咗好多人，但經過孟加拉效應後，大家都記後當晚無死過人<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢個地球咁多人，無時無刻都有人過身，我並不是指明 d 人因某件事而死"},{"pid":"0f33ceb3e47bb1941e219ce46960749dbdfc52f7","tid":422603,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要停止一切捐款</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350dc0e616c07176c52f52dca90e27def220087e","tid":422603,"uid":64146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要停止一切捐款</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無發生過都要比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56957913027842888d91a9598ae9528a5b6324c1","tid":422603,"uid":90863,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":